com.datastrato.gravitino.client

Class GravitinoClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datastrato.gravitino.client.GravitinoClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SupportsMetalakes, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class GravitinoClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements SupportsMetalakes, java.io.Closeable
    Gravitino Client for interacting with the Gravitino API, allowing the client to list, load, create, and alter Metalakes.

    It uses an underlying RESTClient to send HTTP requests and receive responses from the API.
